    import java.util.ArrayList;

public class Test_stack<T> {
   private ArrayList<T> stack = new ArrayList<T>();

   public void push(T i) { 
       stack.add(i); //addëŠ” ArrayListì˜ ê°ì²´

   public T pop() {
